subject: Attn: Mr./Madam
body:
Attn: Mr./Madam
This is to bring to your notice that your 2 consignment trunk boxes left Diplomatic Courier Unit Accra-Ghana yesterday evening at about 10.30pm and the diplomat is in London UK now, his name is Mr. Walter Mike the UN-Diplomat call him on this  Email  
waltermikem@gmail.com
  discuss with him how your consignment will be deliver to you in your home address and get back to the (DCU) Management office Accra-Ghana.
Best Regards
Mr.Abdullai Abubakar
General Manager
DUC Accra-Ghana

subject: Re:   Attn: Mr./Madam
body:
Hello Abubakar,

Thank you for reaching out to me. I appreciate the information about my trunk boxes and the diplomat who is currently in London. Could you please provide me with more details about how the delivery will be arranged? I would like to know the process and any necessary steps I need to take.

Looking forward to your response.

Best wishes,
Jesse
